! A tale about scale

Norbert Hartl  (norbert@apptivegrid.de)

""Abstract:""
Scale is a term often used by people with very different meanings. In software development is one of the big causes for pre-mature optimizations and complexity. After a couple of years since the last talk about how to do projects with pharo here comes an updated version.  

""Bio:""
Norbert Hartl has a long track record of creating and building software projects. Currently he is on a mission to create projects with zero dependencies. He co-founded ApptiveGrid where he is working at the moment. He also co-founded PharoPro. 
